<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1361488" n="1"/>
<opener><lb/><abbr>Illustris.</abbr> et <abbr>Celeber.</abbr> Viro <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolao Bernoulli</rs> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Petrus Antonius Michelotti</rs></opener>
<p><lb/>Tibi gaudeo mihi gratulor quod optima fruoris valetudine
                              <lb/>Vir Amicissime; deinde Tibi maximas refero gratias pro
                              <lb/>iis qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> egregie monuisti super meis scriptis qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> a te
                              <lb/>remissa accepi. Quid faciendum erit si latini <subst><del>hoc</del><add>h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c</add></subst> vocabu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>l<subst><del>um</del><add>a</add></subst> <hi rend="u">heterogeneitas</hi>, <hi rend="u">homogeneitas</hi>, <hi rend="u">homogeneum</hi>, <hi rend="u">hetero<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>geneum</hi> respuent? illis sane Philosophi omnes utun<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tur et ipse <abbr>Celeber.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruus</rs> utitur <rs key="biblio_WIW87HR7" type="biblio"><abbr>Dis.</abbr> de Nutritione</rs>.
                              <lb/>Mutabo ut Tibi lubebit in Latinorum gratiam.
                              <lb/>Quando mones obiectionem esse contra hypothesin,
                              <lb/>dicis quod in ista hypothesi minim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ellipsis ordinat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
                              <lb/>non possunt esse minores diametro ipsarum particu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>larum, quia ipsa minima ordinata major vel saltem
                              <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualis supponitur diametro ipsarum particularum
                              <lb/>cubicarum. Sed ordinat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ad ellipsis diametros aut
                              <lb/>axes pro diametris non sunt <choice><sic>accipiende</sic><corr>accipienda</corr></choice>, id ego sal<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tem opinor. Quid itaque?</p>
<p><lb/>Constituo transmittere ad <abbr>Illustris.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruum</rs> mea
      <lb/><rs type="biblio" key="biblio_M3G2JA79">scripta</rs>, quare Te rogo ut statim <date when="1718-10-29">die Sabat<subst><del>o</del><add>i</add></subst></date> sine ulla
                              <lb/>mora ad eum de hac re scribas petasque ab eodem
                              <lb/>num velit mihi favere, et possibili celeritate lege<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>re mea ipsa scripta annotationes et correctio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nes necessarias prout ipsi libebit addendo. Dic illi
                              <lb/>quod ego Tibi solvam omnes expensas, quas debebit
                              <lb/>facere in accipiendis et remittendis ipsismet meis
      <lb/><rs type="letter" key="biblio_M3G2JA79">scriptis</rs>. Nam statim ac responsum habebis<del> quod po-</del>
<lb/>ego mittam scripta vel per <rs key="place_VER-tirola" type="place">Tyrolym</rs>, vel (si melius<supplied>,</supplied>
<pb facs="1361490" n="2"/>
<lb/>tutius, celeriusque id fieri posset) per <rs key="place_GEO-3173435" type="place">Mediolanum</rs> ad tuum
                              <lb/><rs type="person">amicum</rs><note type="internal"><!-- ToDo: Person recherchieren --></note> qui misit <rs key="biblio_WIW87HR7" type="biblio">Dissertationem de Nutritione</rs> (nam
                              <lb/>rogarem <abbr>Ill.</abbr> <abbr>D.</abbr> Marchionem <rs key="pers_DE-588-1221327275" type="person">Butintrochi</rs>) qui <rs type="person">ami<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cus</rs><del> tu<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></del> tuus <rs key="GeoNamesID" type="place">Basileam</rs> deinde transmitteret. In
                              <lb/>hujusmodi rebus tuo utar consilio. Si <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruus</rs> nolet
                              <lb/>serio huic rei operam impendere poterit saltem spatio
                              <lb/>duorum mensium rem ipsam ad umbilicum deducere
                              <lb/>adeo ut pro mense Februarii aut Martii ego accipiam
                              <lb/>ab ipso scripta jam limata et correcta. Saluta ipsum
                              <lb/>plurimum meo nomine cum Patruele <rs key="pers_DE-588-118656503" type="person">Nicolao</rs>.</p>
<p><lb/>Quod ad <abbr>Cl.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-120379260" type="person">Scheuchzer<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs> pertinet, statim ac <rs key="GeoNamesID" type="place">rure</rs> in <rs key="GeoNamesID" type="place">Urbem</rs>
<lb/>redierit <abbr>Ill.</abbr> et <abbr>Exc.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089922930" type="person">Paschalius</rs> omnia ea <choice><sic>que</sic><corr>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></corr></choice> un<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> para<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>vimus ei dabo insistamque omnibus nervis ut res
                              <lb/>ad optatum finem perducatur. Qua de re certio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rem facito ipsum <abbr>Cl.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-120379260" type="person">Scheuchzerum</rs> eundem meo
                              <lb/>nomine salutando.</p>
<p><lb/><rs key="biblio_M3G2JA79" type="biblio">Pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>notationem</rs><!-- praenotatio = der Titel. Vermutlich ein Arbeitstitel für De separatione fluidorum --> de Structura Glandularum utpote
                              <lb/>anatomicam legendam et emendandam (si opus
                              <lb/>fuerit) misi ad <abbr>Amiciss.<hi rend="sup"><choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></hi></abbr> nostrum <rs key="pers_DE-588-104265264" type="person"><abbr>Jo.</abbr> <abbr>B.</abbr> Morgagnum</rs>
<lb/>qui pro Latinitate etiam libenter favebit. Verum
                              <lb/>si aliqua habebo ad Te spectantia mittam nullo
                              <lb/>habitu respectu ad <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1221327275" type="person">Marchionem</rs>, cui ne adeo te
                              <lb/>subjiciat ut maxima<del>s</del> etiam literarum mearum
                              <lb/>volumina respuas hortor, rogoque. Immaginetur
                              <lb/>sibi quicquid vult, nihil ad nos attinet. Ipsum enim
                              <lb/>amamus, colimusque veris amiciti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> legibus. </p><closer><salute>Vale
                                    <lb/>ergo Vir Amicissime mihique favere perge.</salute> <dateline>Dabam
                                          <lb/><rs key="place_VER-repven" type="place">Venetiis</rs><date when="1718-10-25"><choice><abbr>a. d.</abbr><expan>a dato</expan></choice> 25 <abbr>Oct<subst><del>b</del><add>o</add></subst>br.</abbr> 1718</date></dateline></closer><note hand="pers_DE-588-119166895"><foreign xml:lang="ger"><abbr>Empf.en</abbr> den <date when="1718-10-26">26<hi rend="sup">ten</hi></date>.</foreign></note>
<pb facs="1361491" n="3"/>
